# 1. Create a new project at https://console.cloud.google.com
# 2. Enable Google Sheets API and Google Drive API
# 3. Create a Service Account and download JSON key
# 4. Copy the ENTIRE JSON content into GOOGLE_SHEETS_CREDENTIALS_JSON (single line, escaped quotes)
# 5. Create a new Google Sheet and copy its ID from the URL
# 6. Share the sheet with the service account email (found in the JSON)
